<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,1569,1740]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1605,1631]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Remarks.</emphasis>
The alternating lifecycle was closed and the asexual generation was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y." pageId="18" pageNumber="19" pagination="482 - 489" refId="ref44509" refString="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y. (2019) Heterogony in Cycloneuroterus (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini) from rearing experiments and DNA barcoding. Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 112 (5), 482 - 489. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / saz 035" type="journal article" year="2019">Ide &amp; Abe (2019)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="biology_ecology">
